# RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation)

Build RAG systems with LangChain, LlamaIndex, or custom pipelines. Use vector databases (FAISS, pgvector, Chroma) for retrieval, and local/Ollama models for generation.

## Architecture
1. Document ingestion and chunking
2. Embedding generation (sentence-transformers)
3. Vector storage and indexing
4. Query processing and retrieval
5. Context augmentation and generation
6. Response validation and filtering
